{"id":275167,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-张俊国夫妇起诉黑监狱，南通中院称要请/","date":"2013-01-18T13:30:52Z","modified":"2013-01-18T13:30:52Z","title":"维权网 | 张俊国夫妇起诉黑监狱，南通中院称要请示领导（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>，南通黑监狱受害人张俊国将起诉南通港闸区政府设置黑监狱，向南通中院提交起诉状，请求确认港闸区政府限制张俊国夫妇人身自由的具体行政行为违法，并请求国家赔偿。张俊国夫妇委托倪文华代理。南通中院立案庭法官说，是否能立案要向领导请示。张俊国感到奇怪，是否能立案就看是否符合法律规定，为什么要请示领导呢？南通究竟是法治社会，还是人治社会？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>晚，张国俊夫妇与朋友在南通市崇川区大骨头餐厅聚餐，突然，南通市公安局港闸区警察等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>将聚餐全部押送秦灶派出所，并对张国俊夫妇创办的公司连夜进行查抄，致使该公司至今无法正常生产。派出所对张俊国夫妇审讯后，转入黑监狱继续关押。直至当年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日，张俊国夫妇才得以释放，被非法拘禁达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">69</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张俊国夫妇在黑监狱期间，受尽屈辱和虐待，被迫写了三不保证（不上访、不上网、不接受媒体采访）后，才予以释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在关押期间，徐丽艳夫妇经历了三处黑监狱，即：正和宾馆、转水农庄和北阁宾馆。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张俊国夫妇起诉港闸区政府借办法制教育学习班名义非法限制公民自由，致使张俊国创办的工厂不能正常生产，导致张俊国夫妇无能力向员工发放工资。年关将近，该厂的员工怨声载道。同时，南通黑监狱的暴行也将大白于天下。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WICY9g1io18/UPkcXuTtrVI/AAAAAAAAZVM/Atj8TlQemJE/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%8A%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A4%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-WICY9g1io18/UPkcXuTtrVI/AAAAAAAAZVM/Atj8TlQemJE/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%8A%E8%A2%AB%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%9C%A8%E6%AD%A4%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>张国俊被关押在此宾馆</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-P5Sy6gCuc0E/UPkcZJ2BpKI/AAAAAAAAZVU/tBOkoNggjmw/s1600/%E6%AD%A3%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%90%E4%B8%BD%E8%89%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"191\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-P5Sy6gCuc0E/UPkcZJ2BpKI/AAAAAAAAZVU/tBOkoNggjmw/s320/%E6%AD%A3%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B3%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%90%E4%B8%BD%E8%89%B3%E7%9A%84%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>正和宾馆是关押徐丽艳的黑监狱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}